      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（確かに、今の言葉は写真の雰囲気とも）\n（良くマッチして……いい一枚になりそうだ）",
      "startTime": 213.3666870116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
