      "text": "あ、そうだ……\n今度、サバイバルキャンプに行くことになった……",
      "startTime": 241.4333445231,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "サバイバルキャンプ……？\n普通のキャンプとは違うのか？",
      "startTime": 247.6333445231,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03-szk027.m4a",
      "text": "普通のキャンプに比べて、出来るだけ持って行く道具を\n減らすのがサバイバルキャンプ……",
      "startTime": 253.6000030517,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03-szk028.m4a",
      "text": "さすがに無人島の時ほどハードにはしないけど\nそれでも半自給自足の生活が楽しめる……！",
      "startTime": 260.2000030517,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "それは楽しそうだな。誰と一緒に行くんだ？",
      "startTime": 264.4999828973,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03-szk029.m4a",
      "text": "サニピのみんなで行くことになった……！　怜ちゃんは\n「また行くの？」なんて言いながら……嬉しそうだった",
      "startTime": 272.6666697184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03-szk030.m4a",
      "text": "すみれちゃんやfranさんから学んだことを生かして\n私も、一杯みんなの役に立ちたい……！",
      "startTime": 280.1666697184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03-szk031.m4a",
      "text": "あ……もちろん、お仕事に影響が出ないように\n節度はわきまえてるから……！",
      "startTime": 287.5666697184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "それなら問題ないな。共通の趣味でみんなの絆が\n深まるのは凄く素敵だと思うぞ",
      "startTime": 293.8666697184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03-szk032.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう……\nこれからも、サバイバルの知識を深めて……",
      "startTime": 298.4666697184,
